comments: Fox (SAC) swipes down and avoids making contact to Wall (HOU) during his shot attempt near the rim.
The crew communicated with Replay Center Official Evan Scott and determined the ball did hit the rim.
Holmes (SAC) establishes himself in a legal position in Gordon's (HOU) path and he absorbs the oncoming contact during the screen.
Hield (SAC) maintains a legal guarding position during Harden's (HOU) jump shot attempt.

Wood (HOU) briefly places a hand on the opposite side of Hield's (SAC) body during the screen, but he immediately slides that hand off. Wood's hand does not come to a pause and the contact is marginal.
Harden (HOU) gathers the ball and takes more than two steps before coming to a stop.
Holmes (SAC) is in a wide stance when the leg to leg contact with Harden (HOU) occurs during the screen.
Following the incidental foot to foot contact with his teammate Wall (HOU), Harden (HOU) maintains a legal pivot foot.
Fox (SAC) reaches in and makes contact to Harden's (HOU) arm that affects his FOM.
Holmes (SAC) commits a take foul on Harden (HOU).
Holmes (SAC) establishes himself in a legal position in Tate's (HOU) path. He slightly turns as a result of absorbing the oncoming contact during the pick.
Wall (HOU) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Hield (SAC) following the release of his jump shot attempt.
